{"type": "article", "id": 14546, "title": "给喵星人的玩耍空间", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-07T07:00:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003296IuQ1vKemzk0oREw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t与宠物之间的互动越来越受关注，<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/13840.html\" target=\"_blank\">之前有原研哉牵头为爱犬的房子做了展览</a>，而给喵星人玩耍的空间也需要精心设计。 Papercut Lab 专为喵星人设计了纸板做的架子，一共有五种形状和多种颜色。它们可以像乐高积木一样无限搭建，做成有造型的书架或者茶几，以适应客厅卧室等不同空间。除此之外，纸板的成本很低，能尽情忍受喵星人的魔爪。该产品还在众筹中，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/katris/new-generation-of-modular-cat-accommodations-meet\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142033G5jgYCd0f7Sebl9Z.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"159\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.23382353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261420342QLEWuqamcfodPO3.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"706\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.03823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142034RWADhSen2lXKNG47.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142034QyAMuqbtNJVE2jcz.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"488\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142035dC3jeSuW0P8Lb4mO.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"566\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}